  <!-- ═══ FRE Welcome Page ═══ -->
  <data name="FreOverlay_WelcomeTitle.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Welkom by Intelligent Terminal</value>
    <comment>{Locked=qps-ploc,qps-ploca,qps-plocm} "Intelligent Terminal" is the product name.</comment>
  </data>
  <data name="FreOverlay_WelcomeSubtitlePrefix" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Stel jou ingeboude assistent op om jou te help om foute te verduidelik, opdragte op te stel en take te deblokkeer reg waar jy werk. </value>
  </data>
  <data name="FreOverlay_WelcomeSubtitleLink" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Kom meer te wete oor Intelligent Terminal</value>
    <comment>{Locked=qps-ploc,qps-ploca,qps-plocm} "Intelligent Terminal" is the product name.</comment>
  </data>
  <data name="FreOverlay_Card1Title.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Bly in die vloei met jou ingeboude KI-agent</value>
    <comment>In this context, "agent" refers to an AI agent (e.g. Copilot, Claude, Gemini), not a human agent or representative.</comment>
  </data>
  <data name="FreOverlay_Card1Description.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Jou agent hou dop wat in jou terminaal gebeur en kan jou help om foute te verstaan en reg te stel soos hulle verskyn.</value>
    <comment>In this context, "agent" refers to an AI agent (e.g. Copilot, Claude, Gemini), not a human agent or representative.</comment>
  </data>
  <data name="FreOverlay_Card2Title.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Tel op presies waar jy opgehou het</value>
  </data>
  <data name="FreOverlay_Card2Description.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Hou tred met jou aktiewe en vorige agentsessies en keer binne sekondes terug na jou werk. Hersien wat aan die gang is of herbesoek vroeëre werk sonder om jou plek te verloor.</value>
    <comment>In this context, "agent" refers to an AI agent (e.g. Copilot, Claude, Gemini), not a human agent or representative.</comment>
  </data>
  <data name="FreOverlay_NextButton.Content" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Volgende</value>
  </data>
  <!-- ═══ FRE Settings Page ═══ -->
  <data name="FreOverlay_SettingsTitle.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Welkom by Intelligent Terminal</value>
    <comment>{Locked=qps-ploc,qps-ploca,qps-plocm} "Intelligent Terminal" is the product name.</comment>
  </data>
  <data name="FreOverlay_SettingsSubtitlePrefix" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Kies wat om nou op te stel. Jy kan dit enige tyd verander in </value>
  </data>
  <data name="FreOverlay_SettingsSubtitleLink" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Instellings</value>
  </data>
  <data name="FreOverlay_AgentLabel.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Agent</value>
    <comment>In this context, "agent" refers to an AI agent (e.g. Copilot, Claude, Gemini), not a human agent or representative.</comment>
  </data>
  <data name="FreOverlay_AgentDescription.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Kies die agent-CLI wat in die agentpaneel gebruik word. Enige versoenbare ACP CLI sal outomaties opgespoor word.</value>
    <comment>{Locked="CLI","ACP"}
In this context, "agent" refers to an AI agent (e.g. Copilot, Claude, Gemini), not a human agent or representative.</comment>
  </data>
  <data name="FreOverlay_AgentInstallHint.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>ℹ Hierdie agent benodig Node.js en NPX, wat outomaties geïnstalleer sal word as dit nog nie teenwoordig is nie.</value>
    <comment>{Locked="Node.js","NPX"}
In this context, "agent" refers to an AI agent (e.g. Copilot, Claude, Gemini), not a human agent or representative.</comment>
  </data>
  <data name="FreOverlay_AutoErrorLabel.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Outomatiese foutopsporing</value>
  </data>
  <data name="FreOverlay_AutoErrorDescription.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Gee Intelligent Terminal toestemming om toegang tot jou dop te kry en foute outomaties op te spoor.</value>
    <comment>{Locked=qps-ploc,qps-ploca,qps-plocm} "Intelligent Terminal" is the product name.</comment>
  </data>
  <data name="FreOverlay_SessionLabel.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Sessiebestuur</value>
  </data>
  <data name="FreOverlay_SessionDescription.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Gee Intelligent Terminal toestemming om die status van jou lopende of aktiewe agente na te spoor.</value>
    <comment>{Locked=qps-ploc,qps-ploca,qps-plocm} "Intelligent Terminal" is the product name.
In this context, "agent" refers to an AI agent (e.g. Copilot, Claude, Gemini), not a human agent or representative.</comment>
  </data>
  <data name="FreOverlay_SessionHint.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>ℹ Deur dit te aktiveer, sal integrasie-hake geïnstalleer word om sessies oor jou agent-CLI's na te spoor.</value>
    <comment>{Locked="CLI"}
In this context, "agent" refers to an AI agent (e.g. Copilot, Claude, Gemini), not a human agent or representative.</comment>
